# $Id#

* How to run SQL scripts from this tree:
./deploy-tree-local.sh
cd /tmp/satcon-local-deploy/
sqlplus foo/bar@baz @rhn/tables/rhnChannel.sql

* How to create the satellite schema:
make satellite-clean satellite-devel TBS=DATA_TBS SQLUSER=satdev/satdev@testdb1

* How to build the satellite schema rpm:
cd satellite
make release

* How to bump the schema version:
edit satellite/version

***

* How to build an RHN Satellite upgrade tarball:
# an example:
./build-rhn-satellite-upgrade-2.1-to-4.0.tar.gz.sh \
  rhn-satellite-upgrade-2.1-to-4.0-v1.0.tar.gz
